en_429337_0	Major General Darshana Hettiarrachchi, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna as the chief guest for the commencement of the Army-built Park Joonho International Kindergarten's new semester in the New Year, admitted the first kid to the pre-school on Thursday (10) during a simple ceremony at Siththankerni, Jaffna.
en_429337_1	The Jaffna troops built the new pre-school at the invitation of its founder, Ven Banagala Upathissa Thero of the Yoshida Foundation, considering its importance to the area in September last year.
en_429337_2	The pre-school admitted a group of 50 kids for the new semester during this brief ceremony, attended by a gathering of parents, well-wishers and children.
